text: Maulana Abdul Haq Baloch (5 January 1947-16 March 2010) was a Pakistani Islamic scholar and politician from Kech District, Balochistan. He served as member of the National Assembly of Pakistan from 1985–1988,belongs to Jamat e Islami. ==References== Category:1947 births Category:2010 deaths Category:Baloch people Category:People from Kech District Category:Jamaat-e- Islami Pakistan politicians Category:Pakistani MNAs 1985–1988 Category:Jamia Darul Uloom, Karachi alumni
